<HEADLINE>
FT  27 APR 94 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1994
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By STEVE THOMPSON, CHRIS PRICE and PETER JOHN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (51).
BUILDING &amp; CNSTRN (2) Bett Bros., Shorco, BLDG MATLS &amp; MCHTS (3) Cape,
Johnston, Roskel, CHEMICALS (9) DIVERSIFIED INDLS (4) ELECTRNC &amp; ELECT EQUP
(3) Nokia Prf., Psion, Roxboro, ENGINEERING (3) ASW, Domnick Hunter,
Wellman, ENG, VEHICLES (1) GKN, EXTRACTIVE INDS (5) FOOD MANUF (1) Moran,
