                                                    (American Tobaccco
                                                           subsidiary)
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Tobacco revenues                  Pounds 13.01bn         Dollars 1.5bn
(as per cent of group revenues)    62.7 per cent         10.9 per cent
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Tobacco operating profits          Pounds 1.21bn        Dollars 169.2m
(as per cent of group
 operating profits)                57.8 per cent         11.2 per cent
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
